We're thrilled to announce the early access launch of Gemini Earn! With a Gemini Earn account, you can receive up to 7.4% interest on the crypto you hold with Gemini.

• Interest is earned and compounded daily
• No minimums
• Available in all 50 US states
• No fees when you redeem your crypto

In addition, a new "Watchlist" filter is now available - Users can now create a watchlist of any listed cryptocurrencies and filter for them in the Market tab.
